# Return of the Crimson King

## High Concept
Take up the mantle of Wehat, King of the Highlands and He Who Makes Snow Red! Wield the Winterblade and strike fear into your enemies.

##Genre 
2D Action/Fighting game

##Platform
Desktop browser

##Story
Wehat returned to his domain after a long journey, only to find that his children had been slain and his throne stolen by the vile
Lady Weezalamos! Now, Wehat must take up his sacred sword once again in order to exact his revenge and reclaim his throne.    

##Aesthetics
Cartoon-y animals with dramatic dialogue and clothes remniscent of the cultures in the Himalayas. Lots of cartoon blood.

##Gameplay

### Mechanics
The player controls Wehat, a master of warfare. They can move left and right using the A and D keys and swing their weapon by clicking.

